00:41:21.150 --> 00:41:24.020
Saan ka man magpunta, kailangan mong mag-ingat.

00:41:24.020 --> 00:41:26.270
Nag-aalala ako sayo, Nava.

00:41:29.310 --> 00:41:31.200
